      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes the mechanisms for allowing a JavaScript application to control the signaling plane of a multimedia session via the interface specified in the W3C RTCPeerConnection API and discusses how this relates to existing signaling protocols.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This specification obsoletes RFC 8829.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
